{"tid":703752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中央打救】彭博：傳人行撐海航發債集資","createTime":"2018-06-16T01:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T13:01:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b825b9937aee730eb18eeb2c3bebead4888d5f","tid":703752,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T01:15:09.000Z","msg":"【中央打救】彭博：傳人行撐海航發債集資<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180615/58324150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58324150&d=GTfj4BkWD%2B1rIv3%2F09k5wjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=72f737f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58324150&h=36397561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180615/58324150</a><br />\n<br />\n深陷債務問題的海航集團轉機在望！彭博引述消息人士指，內地領導級官員同意協助海航集團發債集資，又認為海航問題跟安邦和明天集團不同。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士稱，中央政府領導級官員認為海航集團可獲協助，解決融資問題。報道續指，人行高級官員本周二跟海航聯席副主席陳峰、三名監管部人員、海南市政府官員和集團最大債務人會面，人行跟出席會議者下達指示，協助海航集團發債。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，內地領導級官員對協助海航集團發債集資「開綠燈」，主因他們認為海航問題，有別於安邦集團和明天集團，此舉亦替負債逾930億美元的海航集團設下安全網。<br />\n<br />\n此外，內地傳媒引述海航旗下渤海金控公告指，其不超過40億元人民幣公司發債計劃獲中證監審批通過。<br />\n<br />\n睇黎習大大決定幫王歧山<br />\n所有風險要銀行食曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04232d37de975764202799f6652514e7aa8051f","tid":703752,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T01:15:27.000Z","msg":"[贏国冇事嘅] 頭半年16間企業爆煲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/703279/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/703279/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"518cbaeac181736ccd9d6a439ad19be4240bfba2","tid":703752,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T01:16:14.000Z","msg":"有線中國組：中國養老金結餘，只能夠用 17 個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/703250/page/4?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/703250/page/4?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a2bc3b302d7b578e2b39914d53eb6fa11487f0f","tid":703752,"uid":125809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:00:40.000Z","msg":"比錢自己人唔算貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e84aa0efe07fa1b7eac2f2926eb9c040617fdd7","tid":703752,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a2bc3b302d7b578e2b39914d53eb6fa11487f0f","tid":703752,"uid":125809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:00:40.000Z","msg":"比錢自己人唔算貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"俾錢海航繼續炒賣海外資產，不能算貪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b0fbb1ec3e1fc77e1e1b362b2fa8d85809091d","tid":703752,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32df7177b207f38b8350404250e2f02ff201ecb6","tid":703752,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"死撚開啦<br />\n冇人信你D支那債券呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2088aae7d84fb94b0aa64e85b1910b715f5a692a","tid":703752,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:38:58.000Z","msg":"強國可以無限發債，然後唔洗還錢咁"},{"pid":"7284dc2089ecd77a55abc754c4562994d269eb19","tid":703752,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d264c451843f84a016a4b2a6df51e683854cac","tid":703752,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01: